{"tid":1926486,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】研究人員發現病毒或於 0 度下死亡   料未來數星期美國北部、中國東北部成重災區","createTime":"2020-03-15T07:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T07:48:17.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"362bf5005c475c5280003eec592e52afd8b5a63f","tid":1926486,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/6002911_031120-cc-ap-coronavirus-us-washington-img.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F6002911_031120-cc-ap-coronavirus-us-washington-img.jpg&h=b0c5b441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA patient is loaded into an ambulance, Tuesday, March 10, 2020, at the Life Care Center in Kirkland, Wash., near Seattle. The nursing home is at the center of the outbreak of the coronavirus in Washington state. (AP Photo/Ted S. Warren)<br />\n<br />\n隨著全球目前正受武漢肺炎的影響，各國的專家亦逐漸加強研究工作，試圖了解病毒的弱點從而及早消滅。在近日，有研發人員就在全球知名科學研究網站 SSRN 發表報告，指武漢肺炎疫情集中於北半球的一條「走廊地帶」，並預測未來數星期的社區感染可能將會向北移動，預計美國中西部及東北部、加拿大以及中國東北部會成為疫情較嚴重的地區。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/3-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F3-3.jpg&h=092fee00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在 SSRN 上，一個由美國以及伊朗研究人員所組成團隊就發表了迎的研究報告，當中指出目前社區感染向東面及西面發展的模式為一致，新的集中區大概介乎於北緯 30 至 50 度之間，預測未來幾周內的社區感染將有極大可能會出現擴散至美國東北及中西部、加拿大部分省市與中國東北部等地區，呼籲有關的地區政府應準備充足的醫療措施。<br />\n<br />\n此外，研究亦發現引發武漢肺炎的病毒對溫度極為敏感，最佳環境是攝氏 8.72 度，指出目前病毒在一定的溫度和濕度下將可以生效長時間，不要期待天氣變暖時病毒會被消滅。不過，研究團隊就發現，目前低於攝氏零度的城市都沒有受病毒影響，或暗示著病毒將於相關溫度下無法生存，但有關的猜測仍需作進一步的研究。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/03/15/high-temperature-and-high-humidity-reduce-the-transmission-of-covid-19/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F03%2F15%2Fhigh-temperature-and-high-humidity-reduce-the-transmission-of-covid-19%2Flife-tech%2F&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyXG9l5Y5fMjkJfB04Oq%2Bkmk%3D&h=3e5899d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/03/15/high-temperature-and-high-humidity-reduce-the-transmission-of-covid-19/life-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"c221d8a570ea74cc5d94bb24e4e6aae09ba6338d","tid":1926486,"uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:07:54.000Z","msg":"格陵蘭果然係全球最安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0849e74ca3ee991a310a1cabf02e21d76c98f8f8","tid":1926486,"uid":159821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"目前低於攝氏零度的城市都沒有受病毒影響?? 咁北海道呢？"},{"pid":"22e1ee1e357512ba79289bff4f9b42f6f5d2428a","tid":1926486,"uid":35273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:08:36.000Z","msg":"但北海道都出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298a7d0a2ac23008de5770957039971e330f05ac","tid":1926486,"uid":282744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:09:13.000Z","msg":"芬蘭出晒事wo"},{"pid":"94e1c4ad869faf8fe5669ce6c2527a38d7dae21b","tid":1926486,"uid":46493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:09:58.000Z","msg":"係唔係英國研究黎？？"},{"pid":"a06911fc07a531ac6c2d350973fe3716c26fe5e2","tid":1926486,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0849e74ca3ee991a310a1cabf02e21d76c98f8f8","tid":1926486,"uid":159821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"目前低於攝氏零度的城市都沒有受病毒影響?? 咁北海道呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:11:25.000Z","msg":"北海道全年平均溫度係9度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daab64f3d466ed21d112225779aef75deafca896","tid":1926486,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"其實0度人都死，<br />\n唔洗突破盲腸啦